div.p:


Firſt primitive, ye are to behold it, as Chriſt, he who lives for your eternall profit, puts it into action; and ſo, this his life, being unto you the life of a Prieſt; hence it is that in the firſt riſe unto him, from you tithes are due; 

                  〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
               , in that for you he liveth now a Prieſt.
